  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, these datasets lack annotations for opinion terms, a deficiency addressed by the dataset introduced in FAN (2019), designed for target-oriented opinion word extraction (TOWE) tasks.",
    "Xu et al. (2020b) further consolidated these annotations, with slight refinements, to create the ASTE-Data-V1, V2 datasets (Xu et al. 2020a), where each sample sentence contains triples of aspect terms, opinion terms, and sentiment polarities.",
    "More recently, for the ACOSQE task, two new datasets, ACOS (Cai et al. 2021a) and QUAD (Zhang et al. 2021b), have been introduced, with each data instance annotated with four sentiment elements.",
    "To expand the dataset's capacity, the ASQP (Zhang et al. 2023) has released two novel datasets, en-Phone and zh-FoodBeverage.",
    "En-Phone is an English dataset for ACOSQE in the cell phone domain collected from various e-commerce platforms."
  ],
